title: Ted Cruz: 'Lunacy' to strip Iowa of first-in-the-nation status
text:
Published By: Des Moines Register - Today 
U.S. Sen. Ted Cruz called talk of removing Iowa from first place "lunacy" during a town hall in Fort Dodge. ...
